# Pull requests — pre-push checks

Before **`git push`** or **`gh pr create`**:

1. **`npm run ci:fast`** — lint + unit (quick), or **`npm run ci`** for the full GitHub pipeline ([`scripts/ci-local.sh`](../../scripts/ci-local.sh)).
2. **`npm run test:functional`** — when APIs, Prisma, or integrations changed (included in **`npm run ci`**).

Do not open or update a PR until at least **`npm run ci:fast`** exits 0; run **`npm run ci`** before merge when you touched checkout, e2e, or build paths.
